quite a lot of you.

36
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:05,160
But those who are going to stay here

37
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:10,800
have to understand that they are here with a purpose,

38
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:14,600
not without a purpose.

39
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:18,080
And during My absence

40
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:25,000
one should not waste that time.

41
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:31,800
On the contrary, you must put your mind

42
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:41,400
to find out what you can do

43
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:47,280
to improve the

44
