01:38:15,600 --> 01:38:18,280
you don’t feel like eating, all right, forget it. Eat some.

1260
01:38:18,600 --> 01:38:21,600
We have to be wise, we have to be open,

1261
01:38:22,120 --> 01:38:27,120
we are not to be bound by our conditioning from childhood.

1262
01:38:27,760 --> 01:38:29,440
This we must understand,

1263
01:38:29,840 --> 01:38:32,760
that vegetarianism is not going to take you to God,

1264
01:38:32,960 --> 01:38:35,640
neither non-vegetarianism.

1265
01:38:36,840 --> 01:38:40,520
Because the Spirit is neither a vegetarian nor a non-vegetarian.

1266
01:38:40,960 --> 01:38:43,760
It is a detached thing, it’s above food.

1267
01:38:44,200 --> 01:38:47,920
But whatever you need for your body is important.

1268
01:38:48,360 --> 01:38:50,400
If you need protein, eat protein.

1269
01:38:50,680 --> 01:38:53,520
If you don’t eat protein, don’t eat protein,

1270
01:38:53,800 --> 01:38:56,880
but then eat something which you need.

1271
01:38:57,840 --> 01:39:02,480
So it is not that one has to understand it

1272
01:39:03,040 --> 01:39:08,880
in a way that we understand as a chicken and vegetables,

1273
01:39:09,080 --> 01:39:10,960
but we must understand

1274
01:39:11,400 --> 01:39:15,360
in the way a doctor understands, proteins and carbohydrates.

1275
01:39:15,680 --> 01:39:19,120
All right? Whatever you like, you can eat.

1276
01:39:19,720 --> 01:39:23,920
There’s no, in Sahaja Yoga there’s no such a compulsion.

1277
01:39:25,280 --> 01:39:27,640
So many saints used to eat meat.

1278
01:39:27,840 --> 01:39:32,240
So many saints. Guru Nanaka, Kabira, Mohammed-sahib,

1279
01:39:32,720 --> 01:39:36,320
Christ, Rama Himself, Krishna Himself.

1280
01:39:36,520 --> 01:39:40,440
All of them ate meat. Even Buddha ate meat.

1281
01:39:41,240 --> 01:39:44,560
The proof is that, at the end of His life,

1282
01:39:44,960 --> 01:39:49,160
He went to one of His disciples who was a hunter,

1283
01:39:50,360 --> 01:39:53,640
and He told him, “I am very hungry, give Me something to eat.”

1284
01:39:53,880 --> 01:39:56,040
So he said “Sir, I have nothing else but a wild boar

1285
01:39:56,240 --> 01:39:58,800
which I have killed very recently

1286
01:39:59,000 --> 01:40:01,200
and it is not yet fully cooked.”

1287
01:40:01,560 --> 01:40:03,720
So he said, “All right, doesn’t matter I’ll have it,”

1288
01:40:04,040 --> 01:40:07,440
And He ate it and He died because of that

1289
01:40:07,880 --> 01:40:11,600
half-cooked wild boar.

1290
01:40:13,240 --> 01:40:15,040
And He died with that.

1291
01:40:15,280 --> 01:40:18,600
So now Buddhists think that, “We should not eat meat.” It’s not so.

1292
01:40:18,800 --> 01:40:21,960
Because He ate something that was half-cooked,

1293
01:40:22,280 --> 01:40:23,960
That means He did eat, isn’t it?

1294
01:40:24,160 --> 01:40:28,400
Even Jains know that, it’s only Neminath

1295
01:40:29,040 --> 01:40:32,840
who got a kind of a feeling against meat eating.

1296
01:40:33,040 --> 01:40:35,320
That was Neminath, was at the time of,

1297
01:40:35,520 --> 01:40:37,880
he was contemporary of Shri Krishna.

1298
01:40:38,520 --> 01:40:41,560
When his marriage was celebrated he found many birds

1299
01:40:41,760 --> 01:40:44,080
were killed and he felt terrible about it

1300
01:40:44,480 --> 01:40:47,600
and he didn’t want to eat any meat. Was all right.

1301
01:40:47,960 --> 01:40:50,120
It’s all right. If you don’t feel like, don’t eat it.

1302
01:40:50,480 --> 01:40:52,760
But then a cult started.

1303
01:40:53,080 --> 01:40:57,000
But that means till Neminath, means, Jainis are ancient people,

1304
01:40:57,680 --> 01:41:01,320
till Neminath they were eating meat – is a fact.

1305
01:41:03,400 --> 01:41:06,480
So to get attached to some idea

1306
01:41:06,680 --> 01:41:10,200
is not the way you are doing it.

1307
01:41:10,440 --> 01:41:12,880
If you don’t want to eat, just don’t eat it.

1308
01:41:13,120 --> 01:41:17,400
And if somebody has to eat it, because of health purposes

1309
01:41:17,880 --> 01:41:21,120
or because of the need, there’s nothing wrong in it.

1310
01:41:22,120 --> 01:41:24,040
Everybody has a different need,

1311
01:41:24,240 --> 01:41:26,960
every individual has a different need

1312
01:41:28,040 --> 01:41:31,160
If I, personally, take just to vegetarian food,

1313
01:41:31,320 --> 01:41:33,440
I won’t exist I can tell you.

1314
01:41:33,600 --> 01:41:40,280
Because I have such a great capacity to have purges.

1315
01:41:41,080 --> 01:41:43,080
If I meet somebody, shake hands with somebody,

1316
01:41:43,280 --> 01:41:45,240
he has lots of bhoots you see,

1317
01:41:45,440 --> 01:41:49,360
then I just clear him out by purging.

1318
01:41:51,600 --> 01:41:54,960
And if I take just to say, carbohydrates,

1319
01:41:55,080 --> 01:41:56,960
I don’t know what will happen to Me.

1320
01:41:57,160 --> 01:42:00,560
But doesn’t mean that I should be a meat eater,

1321
01:42:00,760 --> 01:42:03,560
but I have to have proteins. That’s the point is.

1322
01:42:03,960 --> 01:42:06,800
It’s no question of meat or anything but this is question

1323
01:42:07,040 --> 01:42:10,320
of eating proteins or carbohydrates.

1324
01:42:11,480 --> 01:42:13,280
We have to be wise about it.

1325
01:42:13,480 --> 01:42:15,360
And all such cults you see,

1326
01:42:15,560 --> 01:42:18,960
that “You eat this, you eat that”, is not so.

1327
01:42:19,360 --> 01:42:21,000
There is no cult in Sahaja Yoga.

1328
01:42:21,160 --> 01:42:24,600
Every individual has  a different personality,

1329
01:42:24,880 --> 01:42:29,120
but, the common thing is one, and that is the Spirit.

1330
01:42:30,000 --> 01:42:35,440
But for example, drinking, we abhor.

1331
01:42:35,640 --> 01:42:38,560
But after Realization, before that I don’t talk of drinking.

1332
01:42:38,920 --> 01:42:42,320
Because it goes against your chaitanya, means your awareness.

1333
01:42:42,680 --> 01:42:45,600
So one has to look after the awareness.

1334
01:42:46,200 --> 01:42:49,360
So much time has been wasted in people in

1335
01:42:49,560 --> 01:42:51,040
deciding what to eat what not to eat.

1336
01:42:51,240 --> 01:42:53,040
What have they achieved? Nothing!

1337
01:42:53,840 --> 01:42:57,360
Sometimes I have seen vegetarians can be horrid people.

1338
01:42:58,280 --> 01:43:03,600
Absolutely horrid. We have a community in India called Marwadis.

1339
01:43:04,680 --> 01:43:08,400
They are blood suckers you see, and they are vegetarians.

1340
01:43:09,480 --> 01:43:13,960
Not all, we have some in Sahaja Yoga also, very few.

1341
01:43:14,760 --> 01:43:19,360
They are extremely money-minded people, you know that.

1342
01:43:20,920 --> 01:43:23,760
So, this kind of thing, to believe that

1343
01:43:23,960 --> 01:43:27,080
such food will make us great is, will be falsehood.

1344
01:43:27,280 --> 01:43:28,920
So you don’t decide on that.

1345
01:43:29,040 --> 01:43:31,880
You decide on proteins and carbohydrates.

1346
01:43:32,480 --> 01:43:36,200
Whatever good for your health, you should do.

1347
01:43:37,000 --> 01:43:40,360
Those who eat too much of vegetarian food

1348
01:43:41,040 --> 01:43:43,280
are liable to certain type of diseases

1349
01:43:43,440 --> 01:43:47,280
and those who eat too much of non-veg are liable to some.

1350
01:43:49,040 --> 01:43:53,880
Those who eat vegetarian food can get leucoderma very easily,

1351
01:43:54,880 --> 01:44:00,520
can get leukemia very easily.

1352
01:44:01,320 --> 01:44:04,920
Certain types of cancers they can get very easily.

1353
01:44:05,200 --> 01:44:08,400
Those who are non-vegetarians can get another kind of diseases.

1354
01:44:08,600 --> 01:44:11,040
There are numerous diseases they can get.

1355
01:44:11,400 --> 01:44:14,040
So we have to have a balance,

1356
01:44:14,240 --> 01:44:17,520
that when we eat vegetarian food also, we must see that we eat

1357
01:44:17,720 --> 01:44:21,880
sufficiently, sufficient amount of proteins,

1358
01:44:23,000 --> 01:44:25,600
because body has to be all right.

1359
01:44:26,040 --> 01:44:30,480
Healthy body is the temple of God,

1360
01:44:30,680 --> 01:44:35,120
and to temple of God, you have to keep it healthy and happy.

1361
01:44:36,040 --> 01:44:39,200
That’s the attitude. But it’s not so important,

1362
01:44:39,560 --> 01:44:41,800
because once you get into Sahaja Yoga, as it is,

1363
01:44:42,000 --> 01:44:45,440
automatically doctors' bill drops to nil.

1364
01:44:45,840 --> 01:44:46,960
Automatically.

1365
01:44:47,440 --> 01:44:50,760
So we have to take a wise attitude towards ourselves.

1366
01:44:51,040 --> 01:44:54,480
Not to torture ourselves because of certain conditionings.

1367
01:44:55,120 --> 01:44:57,160
Because we have been taught something from childhood

1368
01:44:57,280 --> 01:45:00,200
we should not accept it, but see for ourselves.

1369
01:45:00,760 --> 01:45:03,480
I have seen that people who had

1370
01:45:04,000 --> 01:45:06,880
tremendous stigmas about vegetarian food,

1371
01:45:07,080 --> 01:45:10,600
when they took to, say, protein food,

1372
01:45:11,040 --> 01:45:14,000
they improved very much in vibrations. They did.

1373
01:45:14,520 --> 01:45:17,200
Protein food is very important for certain people

1374
01:45:17,560 --> 01:45:19,600
and for certain people carbohydrates.

1375
01:45:19,800 --> 01:45:23,360
Liverish people should take to carbohydrates.

1376
01:45:24,880 --> 01:45:29,040
It is absolutely an open thing for us to understand.

1377
01:45:29,760 --> 01:45:33,600
But whatever goes against our awareness,

1378
01:45:33,840 --> 01:45:38,200
because in our own awareness we have to achieve our Spirit,

1379
01:45:39,640 --> 01:45:41,720
we drop out that, also, very easily.

1380
01:45:41,920 --> 01:45:44,160
I don’t have to say that, “Don’t drink! Don’t smoke!”

1381
01:45:44,360 --> 01:45:46,360
You just drop out.

1382
01:45:49,440 --> 01:45:55,720
Mother, Bernard Shaw, a very distinguished Irish writer

1383
01:45:55,920 --> 01:45:58,920
apparently once said that he doesn’t like his stomach

1384
01:45:59,120 --> 01:46:01,800
to be graveyard out of dead animals.

1385
01:46:02,000 --> 01:46:05,200
Now Bernard Shaw did not give Realization to anyone, did he?

1386
01:46:05,360 --> 01:46:07,640
He was very great and a vegetarian.

1387
01:46:07,800 --> 01:46:09,560
You see, he might become vegetarian

1388
01:46:09,760 --> 01:46:12,360
doesn’t mean that everybody should, is it?

1389
01:46:13,080 --> 01:46:16,960
It’s not a graveyard. I tell you, it’s not a graveyard.

1390
01:46:17,160 --> 01:46:19,920
He must be constipated.

1391
01:46:22,280 --> 01:46:25,880
That’s all I can say. You see Bernard Shaw,

1392
01:46:26,080 --> 01:46:28,880
is all right whatever he said. According to his own is correct.

1393
01:46:29,080 --> 01:46:31,320
For him it may be.

1394
01:46:32,120 --> 01:46:34,560
You see most of the vegetarians

1395
01:46:34,760 --> 01:46:36,840
have a problem and non-vegetarians have a problem.

1396
01:46:37,040 --> 01:46:39,280
I have seen it every day in My life.

1397
01:46:39,640 --> 01:46:41,520
Today is not Bernard Shaw here, otherwise

1398
01:46:41,640 --> 01:46:44,000
I would have told him what he suffered from.

1399
01:46:44,200 --> 01:46:48,880
You see it is, whatever they express in their individual experience.

1400
01:46:49,280 --> 01:46:53,000
All right? I am not expressing an individual experience,

1401
01:46:53,280 --> 01:46:57,840
I am giving you an experience of many. All right?

1402
01:46:58,040 --> 01:47:00,720
I get your point that one should eat proteins.

1403
01:47:00,920 --> 01:47:03,640
Are you saying that vegetarian food doesn’t have proteins?

1404
01:47:03,800 --> 01:47:08,880
What is it? Yes, you can. So you should eat. When did I say no?

1405
01:47:10,560 --> 01:47:13,320
I never said, that if you can eat, eat proteins, finished.

1406
01:47:13,560 --> 01:47:16,680
It should be decided on proteins and carbohydrates,

1407
01:47:16,840 --> 01:47:20,360
and not on all these things because nobody dies.

1408
01:47:23,000 --> 01:47:27,640
You see, we have no compassion for our own fellow being.

1409
01:47:29,520 --> 01:47:34,560
Where are we? We have no compassion for our own relations,

1410
01:47:34,760 --> 01:47:36,680
our own father, our own mother,

1411
01:47:36,880 --> 01:47:41,080
our own brothers and sisters and other people.

1412
01:47:41,960 --> 01:47:45,280
And what’s the use of having compassion on things

1413
01:47:45,480 --> 01:47:48,080
which do not understand at all?

1414
01:47:48,360 --> 01:47:53,160
And they don’t need it! Who needs compassion, are human beings,

1415
01:47:53,600 --> 01:47:55,720
who are aware of it.

1416
01:47:57,600 --> 01:48:00,880
It is too far fetched, and that is very true with human mind,

1417
01:48:01,080 --> 01:48:03,520
because they want to shift their mind to something

1418
01:48:03,840 --> 01:48:05,760
which will take them away from Reality.

1419
01:48:05,960 --> 01:48:08,720
Like the other day I told somebody not to feel guilty

1420
01:48:08,920 --> 01:48:11,120
because they were catching on the Left Vishuddhi.

1421
01:48:11,400 --> 01:48:14,160
And she said, “I feel guilty”. I said, “For what?”

1422
01:48:14,360 --> 01:48:16,800
“I feel guilty for Vietnam”. I said “For what?”

1423
01:48:17,000 --> 01:48:18,960
“Because the people are dying in Vietnam,”

1424
01:48:19,160 --> 01:48:22,080
I said, “Are you going to solve the problem of Vietnam?

1425
01:48:22,480 --> 01:48:26,680
Are you concerned with it? Why are you worried about that?”

1426
01:48:27,640 --> 01:48:32,080
You do whatever is good for you,

1427
01:48:32,800 --> 01:48:37,000
and what you can do. This is how we shift our mind.

1428
01:48:37,200 --> 01:48:41,320
And it’s very true, you see. People have their accepted ideas,

1429
01:48:41,560 --> 01:48:45,400
they stick onto it, and get nothing.

1430
01:48:47,920 --> 01:48:51,480
So I say that there should be no ‘ism’ about anything.

1431
01:48:51,680 --> 01:48:54,320
You must have an open mind.

1432
01:48:55,400 --> 01:48:59,280
Absolutely an open mind.

1433
01:49:01,080 --> 01:49:04,600
Anybody who, whatever problems they have,

1434
01:49:05,280 --> 01:49:08,200
they know, and they should solve it.

1435
01:49:11,080 --> 01:49:15,280
I am not here to spread vegetarianism or non-vegetarianism,

1436
01:49:15,880 --> 01:49:18,360
I am here to spread Sahaja Yoga.

1437
01:49:18,520 --> 01:49:22,200
"Sahaja Samadhi Lago”. That’s what is said.

1438
01:49:22,480 --> 01:49:25,200
You have to get your samadhi.

1439
01:49:25,720 --> 01:49:29,720
And that how do you get? Sahaj, spontaneous.

1440
01:49:31,840 --> 01:49:34,760
It depends, it depends what we eat, you see.

1441
01:49:35,600 --> 01:49:39,960
How will we get samadi if we do not have proper food or anything?

1442
01:49:40,240 --> 01:49:43,160
Now, I will say that, I’ve already told you about Buddha.

1443
01:49:43,360 --> 01:49:47,520
What do you think of Guru Nanak?
What do you think of Christ?

1444
01:49:47,720 --> 01:49:50,560
You think, were they any way lower?

1445
01:49:50,760 --> 01:49:54,600
You see because the Spirit is not concerned. As Krishna has said,

1446
01:49:54,760 --> 01:49:58,200
"Nainam chindanti shastrani nainam dahati pavakah

1447
01:49:58,360 --> 01:50:02,160
na chainam kledayanty apo na sosayati marutah". (meaning: The Spirit cannot be cut or burned, nor moistened nor blown)

1448
01:50:02,360 --> 01:50:06,200
It is Shri Krishna himself has said it.

1449
01:50:06,600 --> 01:50:09,480
And He Himself has killed rakshasas and Jainis are against

1450
01:50:09,680 --> 01:50:12,040
Shri Krishna because He killed rakshashas.

1451
01:50:12,360 --> 01:50:15,280
According to him He’s a hinsatmak (aggressive) fellow.

1452
01:50:15,520 --> 01:50:18,320
If you go too far with it, then you go to that limit,

1453
01:50:18,520 --> 01:50:22,480
where you start saving bugs and mosquitoes.

1454
01:50:23,200 --> 01:50:26,880
But we have got it, we have got Realization, no doubt about it.

1455
01:50:27,560 --> 01:50:31,200
First of all you get your Realization. You have had all these ideas,

1456
01:50:31,520 --> 01:50:34,440
all our forefathers had these ideas, they never got Realization.

1457
01:50:34,680 --> 01:50:38,080
All right? So forget it. First thing is get to your Spirit.

1458
01:50:38,280 --> 01:50:41,560
This is not important, this is just you are directing your attention

1459
01:50:41,760 --> 01:50:44,280
to something else which is not important.

1460
01:50:44,880 --> 01:50:50,960
So many of them. So we discard Mohammed-sahib, we discard everyone.

1461
01:50:51,960 --> 01:50:55,440
That’s how it is, it’s Brahmanism,

1462
01:50:57,280 --> 01:51:00,560
it's Brahmanism. It’s ‘ism’ again.

1463
01:51:00,920 --> 01:51:04,480
We discard all the great people of the world by this.

1464
01:51:05,680 --> 01:51:08,320
They were not realized? Kahlil Gibran was he not realized?

1465
01:51:08,520 --> 01:51:10,920
How will you know?

1466
01:51:11,160 --> 01:51:12,720
Unless and until you are realized

1467
01:51:12,880 --> 01:51:14,840
you will not know who is realized or not.

1468
01:51:15,000 --> 01:51:18,280
You will live on these ideas only.

1469
01:51:18,960 --> 01:51:22,560
You have to feel it. William Blake, was he not realized?

1470
01:51:23,560 --> 01:51:26,240
He was Markandeya Himself.

1471
01:51:28,480 --> 01:51:32,640
We have forgotten so many things. Even in the Indian Scriptures

1472
01:51:32,840 --> 01:51:35,760
we never see, we don’t want to see these things.

1473
01:51:36,840 --> 01:51:40,680
We had a great saint in India, called Sajan Kasai.

1474
01:51:46,720 --> 01:51:50,800
So one should understand, that in Sahaja Yoga,

1475
01:51:51,200 --> 01:51:56,480
whatever is the Reality, we try to accept. See for yourself.

1476
01:51:57,040 --> 01:52:00,200
What about your vibrations? Are you getting vibrations or not?

1477
01:52:00,400 --> 01:52:03,280
That’s the main point is. Attention should be there.

1478
01:52:03,520 --> 01:52:06,160
Actually vegetarians have much more attention on food

1479
01:52:06,280 --> 01:52:08,640
than the non-veg have. I can tell you this fact.

1480
01:52:08,840 --> 01:52:11,720
And the women of vegetarian people

1481
01:52:11,920 --> 01:52:15,840
are all the time busy, what to make for their men.

1482
01:52:16,520 --> 01:52:19,560
All the time they are planning what to have

1483
01:52:19,760 --> 01:52:21,680
“Aaj papad banaye ki falana banaye ki…?”

1484
01:52:21,880 --> 01:52:24,440
They are all the time busy cooking, cooking, cooking.

1485
01:52:25,040 --> 01:52:28,480
And the men are also all the time fussing about food.

1486
01:52:28,840 --> 01:52:30,840
“In that house I ate that karela.

1487
01:52:31,000 --> 01:52:34,000
In that house I ate this, you better make that.”

1488
01:52:34,520 --> 01:52:36,760
All our Indian men I know too well.

1489
01:52:36,960 --> 01:52:40,080
And I know all the vegetarians. I am from that country.

1490
01:52:40,520 --> 01:52:43,040
And the women are busy with that and men are busy with that.

1491
01:52:43,240 --> 01:52:46,760
All their attention is in food all the time.

1492
01:52:48,040 --> 01:52:51,480
Women want to cook and men want to enjoy.

1493
01:52:52,120 --> 01:52:53,120
That’s not the way.

1494
01:52:53,560 --> 01:52:55,720
Remove your attention from food, it’s not important.

1495
01:52:55,920 --> 01:52:58,680
Whatever you are eating is all right. Have a balanced diet.

